					<span class="meta-date"><a href="https://advising.uic.edu/share-with-students/" title="SHARE WITH STUDENTS: UIC&#8217;s new Art Education Program &#8211; are you interested?" rel="bookmark">
						<span class="month">Dec</span>
						<span class="day">15</span>
						<span class="year">2017</span>
					</a></span>


					

					<span class="meta-author"><span>by jvolpe</span></span>

				</div>
                
				<div class="post-contents">
										<h3 class="entry-title">
					<a href="https://advising.uic.edu/share-with-students/" title="SHARE WITH STUDENTS: UIC&#8217;s new Art Education Program &#8211; are you interested?" rel="bookmark">SHARE WITH STUDENTS: UIC&#8217;s new Art Education Program &#8211; are you interested?</a>
					</h3>
                    					    <div class="post-category">Posted in <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/advising-weekly-updates/">Advising Weekly Updates</a>, <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/share-with-students/">Share with Students</a></div>
                    					<div class="post-content">
					<p><strong>Looking For a Way to Give Back to the Community? <em>Learn to Teach Art in Chicago Public Schools!</em></strong></p>
<p><strong>HERE’S WHY:</strong><br />
• You can become a licensed high school art teacher.<br />
• The starting full time salary of Chicago Public School teachers is $50,000.<br />
• The job comes with health care, benefits, sick days, and ongoing professional development.<br />
• You&#8217;ll have a chance to impact the community you come from.</p>
<p><strong>UIC’s Art Education </strong>program is accepting applications for the Pre-Art Education cohort<strong> NOW. </strong>The deadline is<strong> January 12, 2018.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://advising.uic.edu/files/2017/12/ArtEd-Recruitment-Poster.pdf">Dowload the flyer to share with your students!</a></p>
<p>Find out more: <a href="http://artandarthistory.uic.edu/art-ed">artandarthistory.uic.edu/art-ed</a><br />
Questions? <a href="mailto:arted@uic.edu">arted@uic.edu</a></p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<br class="clear" />

