				<div class="post-contents">
										<h3 class="entry-title">
					<a href="https://advising.uic.edu/professional-development-class-scheduler-overview-and-demo-slides-are-available/" title="PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: Class Scheduler Overview and Demo Slides are available." rel="bookmark">PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: Class Scheduler Overview and Demo Slides are available.</a>
					</h3>
                    					    <div class="post-category">Posted in <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/advising-weekly-updates/">Advising Weekly Updates</a>, <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/professional-development/">Professional Development</a></div>
