<p>Class Scheduler is a tool that students use to build the optimal schedule based on course preferences and setting aside time for breaks during the week.   Students use Class Scheduler to generate the class schedule that fits their schedule.  OAD and OSSS recently partnered together to host an overview and demo of the Class Scheduler.</p>
<p><a href="https://advising.uic.edu/files/2017/12/Class-Schedulerdemo.pdf">You can now download the slides and directions for using the Class Scheduler.</a></p>
